ca.uqac.lif.ecp.graphs

Class ForestNode<T extends Event>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.ecp.graphs.ForestNode<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of event of the underlying vertices of the Cayley graph

    public class ForestNode<T extends Event>
extends java.lang.Object
    Node in a spanning tree, as used in the union find algorithm for computing the minimum spanning tree of a graph.

    NOTE: the code for the spanning tree has been adapted to Java from Giulio Bottazzi's C implementation.
